## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **teprotumumab Tepezza 2020** = first FDA Thyroid Eye Disease (TED) IGF-1R mAb. Graves ophthalmopathy proptosis + diplopia 임상 paradigm shift. hearing-loss + hyperglycemia 부작용 → 2nd-gen selective Fab 가 hxq-endo2-tepezza-002 candidate. quantum-VQE 의 IGF-1R / IR cross-reactivity 가 직접 fit.
2. **osilodrostat Isturisa 2020** = first oral 11β-hydroxylase inhibitor Cushing. metyrapone 의 oral 후속 + ketoconazole hepatotoxicity 회피. quantum-VQE 의 CYP11B1 vs CYP11B2 selectivity (aldosterone synthase off-target) 가 next falsifier.
3. **setmelanotide Imcivree 2020 → BBS 2022** = first MC4R agonist monogenic obesity (POMC/LEPR/PCSK1 → BBS). melanocortin pathway → cross-obesity + cross-pediatric_rare. quantum-VQE 의 MC4R GPCR pocket leverage.
4. **pasireotide Signifor 2012** = SSTR5/2 multi-receptor analog Cushing + acromegaly. octreotide/lanreotide SSTR2 dominant 와 receptor profile 차이. quantum-VQE 의 SSTR family selectivity.
5. **selpercatinib + pralsetinib 2020** = RET-selective MTC + RET-fusion thyroid Ca. multikinase lenvatinib/sorafenib 의 selective successor. cross-cancer (NSCLC RET) + MEN2 inherited cross-link.
6. **mifepristone Korlym 2012 + relacorilant research** = Cushing GR antagonist axis. mifepristone PR cross-reactivity → relacorilant CORT125134 selective GR 가 next-gen. quantum-VQE 의 nuclear receptor selectivity.
7. **rhPTH Natpara recall 2024 reissue** = HypoP 만성 hypocalcemia + 신장칼슘낭비 자가관리 한계. recombinant PTH 1-84 stability + immunogenicity issues → reissue 후속 quality. quantum-VQE 의 PTHR1 binding mode.
8. **cinacalcet 2004 + etelcalcetide 2017** = CaSR allosteric calcimimetic 2차 HPT (HD). small-mol vs IV peptide 두 modalities. quantum-VQE 의 GPCR allosteric site.
9. **LA-GH (somapacitan 2020 + lonapegsomatropin 2021 + somatrogon 2023)** = weekly GH replacement adult+pediatric paradigm shift. daily injection compliance 향상. WEAVE PEG/Fc/albumin scaffold cross-link.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, thyroid + pituitary + adrenal + parathyroid 임상 의미 한정.

